This paper deals with the problem of updating logic programs, which is a topic that falls under the area of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of formal semantics, which is a topic in mathematical logic (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper involves manipulating and updating databases of knowledge, which is a topic in database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses natural language processing and the use of rules to represent knowledge, which are topics in computational linguistics (cs.CL). Finally, the paper involves examining the computational complexity of different approaches, which is a topic in computational complexity theory (cs.CC).
